headline: Brown-Forman Corporation (BF-B) Nears 52-Week Low as Truist Lowers PT
summary: Brown-Forman Corporation (NYSE:BF-B) is an alcoholic beverage manufacturer and seller. It is known for brands like Jack Daniel’s, Woodford Reserve, and Diplomatico.
